      <title>Salesforce 的新 AI 战略承认 AI 将取代人类工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/salesforce-ai-agent-strategy-acknowledges-job-losses-from-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Salesforce Inc. 本周在其年度 Dreamforce 大会上公布了其人工智能战略的转变，称其人工智能工具可以在没有人工监督的情况下处理任务，并改变了其软件收费方式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/salesforce-ai-agent-strategy-acknowledges-job-losses-from-tech</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
